<span id="freeTextContainer16963222897467800884"> What I love most about her novels is the way she writes. Simply, captivating! But, the problem with Ahlam as an author is the repetitions! I&apos;ve read two of her novels and It&apos;s always the same story, same characters, same ending! I was bored half way through! Hence, the rating of three stars.</span>
  <span id="freeText16963222897467800884" style="display:none"> What I love most about her novels is the way she writes. Simply, captivating! But, the problem with Ahlam as an author is the repetitions! I've read two of her novels and It's always the same story, same characters, same ending! I was bored half way through! Hence, the rating of three stars.</span>
