    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3021884785" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer22317284510053122">Just finished reading &quot;Memory In the Flesh&quot; by Ahlam Mosteghanemi. <br/><br/>As Algeria&apos;s most important female writer, she offers an insight into this former French colony from a unique perspective as the daughter of one of the heroes of the Algerian Revolution. <br/><br/>As well as a different take than we would be offered by combatants on either side, her writings are a milestone as she is the first successful female novelist to write in Arabic (as my mastery of the language is virtually non-existent, I have had</span>
  <span id="freeText22317284510053122" style="display:none">Just finished reading "Memory In the Flesh" by Ahlam Mosteghanemi. <br /><br />As Algeria's most important female writer, she offers an insight into this former French colony from a unique perspective as the daughter of one of the heroes of the Algerian Revolution. <br /><br />As well as a different take than we would be offered by combatants on either side, her writings are a milestone as she is the first successful female novelist to write in Arabic (as my mastery of the language is virtually non-existent, I have had to settle for an English translation.) <br /><br />I appreciate having had the opportunity to gain a bit more understanding of this complex relationship between France and Algeria. Now, back to Steinbeck with "The Wayward Bus' from 1947.</span>
  <a data-text-id="22317284510053122" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

