              <span id="reviewTextContainer3834399223" class="readable"
                    style="display:none"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4202537330991294112">Absolutely Amazing I liked her style in writing, all the feelings and how she expressed them. Ahlem Mostghanmi has a unique way of describing what is felt with th heart and I absolutely adore it. I like how she talked about Algeria&apos;s History and the revolution, also how each caracter had its own background story. I also liked the mystery in hiding the truth behind the relationship between Ziad and Hayet; although I am a 100% sure that they fell in love with each other and she somehow cheated on </span>
  <span id="freeText4202537330991294112" style="display:none">Absolutely Amazing I liked her style in writing, all the feelings and how she expressed them. Ahlem Mostghanmi has a unique way of describing what is felt with th heart and I absolutely adore it. I like how she talked about Algeria's History and the revolution, also how each caracter had its own background story. I also liked the mystery in hiding the truth behind the relationship between Ziad and Hayet; although I am a 100% sure that they fell in love with each other and she somehow cheated on Khaled with Ziad. I love how Ahlem describes Costantine, She shows her love for Algeria in a very unique style.</span>
